Could you provide some more reasoning? I don&#x27;t follow.<p>Maybe the article phrased this sentence wrong, but I think the basis is true. Anyone who has tried to find accurate information about drugs on the Internet has likely visited Erowid.<p>As some evidence I&#x27;ve tried some queries I might search if I wanted to learn more about psychedelic drugs. Erowid is on the first page of Google results for: 
